OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FFrance warns people off    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FBlack Friday clothes deals 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The French government has launched a   
OL,6, campaign encouraging people not to buy 
OL,7, new clothes in Black Friday sales.     
OL,9,FThe advert shows a man asking for      
OL,10,Fadvice in a shop before an assistant   
OL,11,Ftells him not to buy anything, to help 
OL,12,Fthe planet and his finances.           
OL,14,FThe minister for ecological transition 
OL,15,F- responsible for promoting            
OL,16,Fsustainability - Christophe Bechu, is  
OL,17,Fbehind the campaign.                   
OL,19,FBut the message has been criticised by 
OL,20,Fother government departments.          
